:2031783,"uid":304769,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:50:32.000Z","msg":"大家自己執生，記得be water<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOQomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=d7d64f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"b02ccf84597668df3c01f14f5d239c3ef76d76e1","tid":2031783,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e3c68fd4e49e04b7eee6bb8219b39aa91582c6","tid":2031783,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bf7a78a034b0b4c054ae1a5830a4e4edb595a6","tid":2031783,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c80832287ba58cdcd2d49525eed649b3efcf03","tid":2031783,"uid":197235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:57:44.000Z","msg":"無事先做到世界冠軍<br />\n                         -曼德拉"},{"pid":"6bee23fe063fd8b6df2fa516dfbbf66a5e30e5d4","tid":2031783,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20985f6a05732a2c6ffd233056c6950f03c4aab","tid":2031783,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d42362de8648e1ec62ef12519141597b53ffe14","tid":2031783,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"Plan B<br />\n人鏈正吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBe water my friends<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謹記適時保持兩米距離排排企<br />\n我鍾意排隊等巴士<br />\n排隊食黃店<br />\n企定定睇熱鬧<br />\n地少人多，閒閒地都<br />\n1000人、10000人、100000人、1000000人<br />\n隊形痴埋一齊都好正常<br />\n<br />\n文宣係咩？紙囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加卡版、咪變硬卡紙囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天口熱、撥下涼姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗狗鍾意票控咪由得佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抄佢老母票、抄到佢天荒地老<br />\n彌敦道出九龍大老山隧道獅子山入口再出港島太平山<br />\n同我罰抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抄到無紙<br />\n呃佢老母ot錢<br />\n法庭忙到甩轆<br />\n最後原來得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜都唔洗罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾意講咩玩咩都係自由意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個post令我明白p牌嘅價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n秒獲負皮，明明得我自彈自唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多一個人理就即刻放負一隻<br />\n<br />\n證明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吖媽我得左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五毛加持嘅大絕<br />\n使出香港人大技-人海戰術<br />\n排排企食果果<br />\n破佢老母限聚令<br />\n<br />\n兄弟努力 各自爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2031264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2031264</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n反其道而行，先係破局<br />\n同狗玩數字遊戲無意思<br />\n要玩就黎舖曬冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n負皮4<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b700285d8c0ab2e4579f27cd104328a4184bbcef","tid":2031783,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179c65043467d2abcf28f19646a6d68af134246b","tid":2031783,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no